Author: livipup
Text: It does make sense. She must be way smaller than I realized if that's the case though. Even at my lowest weight I wasn't nearly thin enough for my veins to pop out like that.

Author: nintentions
Text: i know EXACTLY who you’re talking about - saw the video this morning. i think veins would start to protrude when you reach a seriously low weight, like there literally isn’t enough fat in her arms to cover the veins if that makes sense
